@startuml
title UC10 - View Profile History Sequence
actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Profile API" as API
participant "Profile Service" as Svc
database "DB" as DB
User -> UI : Open profile/history
UI -> API : GET /me/profile
API -> Svc : getOwnProfile(userId)
Svc -> DB : load user and predictions
DB --> Svc : profile and history
Svc --> API : ProfileDto
API --> UI : 200 OK / 404
UI --> User : Display profile or message
@enduml
